and become nicotine-dependent.</i>

220
00:19:26,090 --> 00:19:29,550
<i>"I am just joking,
because, of course,</i>

221
00:19:30,010 --> 00:19:34,760
<i>"it is impossible for a cigarette
to remain lit underwater.</i>

222
00:19:34,760 --> 00:19:40,390
<i>"Also, fish do not have pockets
to keep cigarette lighters in.</i>

223
00:19:44,410 --> 00:19:48,460
<i>"I am 44 years old
and have eight tracksuits</i>

224
00:19:48,710 --> 00:19:53,530
<i>"the same colour and size.</i>

225
00:19:53,530 --> 00:19:56,260
<i>I weigh 352 pounds..."</i>

226
00:19:56,850 --> 00:19:57,670
Ooh!

227
00:19:57,670 --> 00:20:00,420
<i>"And am as tall
as a six-foot tree."</i>

228
00:20:01,050 --> 00:20:03,300
<i>Welcome to the New York Lottery.</i>

229
00:20:03,300 --> 00:20:05,600
<i>"I enjoy entering the lottery</i>

230
00:20:05,710 --> 00:20:09,010
<i>"and have chosen
the same numbers for nine years.</i>

231
00:20:09,040 --> 00:20:12,370
<i>- Those numbers are 3..."
